name: Mekkana
bio: Daughter of Mekkane, Goddess of modernity, progress and intellect! Looking for a smart, innovative and creative partner to build a future together.

name: Athena
bio: Goddess of wisdom and strategic warfare. Let's have some intellectual battles!

name: Hera
bio: Queen of the gods. Looking for someone who can keep up with divine drama.

name: Aphrodite
bio: Goddess of love and beauty. Swipe right for an unforgettable romance!

name: Persephone
bio: Queen of the Underworld. Can you handle the dark and mysterious?
